cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM 

The paper deals with multimodal search and retrieval, specifically the understanding of semantic cross-modal relations between image and text. This suggests that the paper could belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) or natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper introduces a new metric and uses deep learning, which could also place it in the information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), or multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
